  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 71,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Date'], format='%d/%m/%Y')\n",
    "df['Global_active_power'] = pd.to_numeric(df['Global_active_power'], errors='coerce')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 33,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "daily_data = df.groupby('Date').agg({'Global_active_power': 'sum'}).reset_index()\n",
    "daily_data.columns = ['ds', 'y']\n",
    "\n",
    "total_days = daily_data.shape[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "train_size = total_days - 300\n",
    "train_data = daily_data.iloc[:train_size]\n",
    "test_data = daily_data.iloc[train_size:]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 35,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "17:48:44 - cmdstanpy - INFO - Chain [1] start processing\n",
      "17:48:44 - cmdstanpy - INFO - Chain [1] done processing\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "model = Prophet(daily_seasonality=True)\n",
    "model.fit(train_data)\n",
    "\n",
    "future_dates = model.make_future_dataframe(periods=300)\n",
    "\n",
    "forecast = model.predict(future_dates)\n",
    "\n",
    "forecast_test = forecast[['ds', 'yhat']].tail(300)\n",
    "\n",
    "test_data = test_data.merge(forecast_test, on='ds')"
   ]
  },
